{"tid":211160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘站內玩花式單車 乘客：冇家教不知所謂","createTime":"2017-04-21T12:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T22:47:26.000Z","uid":48093,"like":10,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cec8d1b0f30cb85d26bdbdc9bd9480ef2eec2944","tid":211160,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170421/large/1492767768_df64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170421%2Flarge%2F1492767768_df64.jpg&h=1e446780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170421/large/1492766239_7036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170421%2Flarge%2F1492766239_7036.jpg&h=877af06a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日下午4時許，讀者劉小姐在港鐵金鐘站行經港島綫通往荃灣綫月台的通道時，赫見4名青年聯群結隊前進，當中一人更踩踏著單車，至少兩次連車跳起及轉身一圈，做出「花式表演」，儼如將港鐵變成遊樂場，嚇得其他乘客要側身避開。劉小姐指他們進入車廂後仍未見收斂，旁若無人般放聲喧嘩，並粗言穢語交談，劉小姐形容他們「冇家教、不知所謂，全無公民意識」。<br />\n「個個都驚咗佢，避開晒！」劉小姐指當時見該名孭著背囊及戴帽的青年在通道上玩花式，同伴沒有阻止之餘，還稱讚他「WOW、好型！好正！」但她認為這行為危險有可能會撞及其他乘客，「邊有理由會喺月台踩單車，喺港鐵單車都要拆轆㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n進入車廂後，該青年將單車反轉擱在扶手柱旁，佔去了大部分空間。有人一度取出手機大聲傾談，指正往旺角途中，當中夾雜粗言穢語；有人亦用電話「開Speaker」播歌。劉小姐認為他們是一班「好曳」的青年。<br />\n根據港鐵附例，表明任何人不得在任何時間將任何單車帶過、傳過、駛過或引領其橫過鐵路處所或任何部分。乘客如欲攜帶單車乘搭港鐵，必須於入閘前作出適當處理，例如摺合單車或拆除單車車轆，並妥善包紮，以確保安全及符合運載行李的規定。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人回應，一直為顧客提供安全舒適服務，呼籲乘客上車時要顧及其他乘客，不要做出影響他人行為，若有乘客見到有關情況可通知港鐵職員，以便作出適切跟進。發言人稱單車拆轆後可以進入車廂，港鐵藉此呼籲單車客要小心及顧及其他乘客，可在較少人的車尾上車，亦應注意安全，至於其行為有否違反《港鐵附例》，發言人稱要視現場實際情況而定，不能一概而論。"},{"pid":"3f82fcfa9e1fa0578a98058b569e7ee3a3b94b32","tid":211160,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"如果係外國白人玩，條港女會點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b3da041f1105d7665ef39dbaa60763d19cc80c","tid":211160,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:34:04.000Z","msg":"白鬼做就好型"},{"pid":"f03c372f9191010b3706b457cf41fda6c68622e0","tid":211160,"uid":74385,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:36:59.000Z","msg":"先唔講個港女有無問題, <br />\n<br />\n咁個單車仔又有無做錯先?"},{"pid":"3db2b241c59eae0cce5efc66ddeef5dcb621f5e6","tid":211160,"uid":18988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:38:52.000Z","msg":"小事化大，後生仔緊係貪玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 老餅"},{"pid":"9d57f5447da7d4578cc895438ee532eea007d728","tid":211160,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:44:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca5090937c8313b88f072125cccd87a3cb37056e","tid":211160,"uid":2510,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"是但啦，反正啲憤世仇恨港女既連登仔實拉鬼佬落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cf392672b8753ece30946c9b6cc5f2e4bca45b","tid":211160,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>白鬼做就好型</blockquote><br />\n如果係白人做，個位小姐即刻幫佢含啦</blockquote><br />\n你錯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就呢位咁有公民教養意識，我好理由相信會講「May I」先，然後先追住嚟含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb3629b33f10c3d345575135179e95132d316f8","tid":211160,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:49:46.000Z","msg":"白人 &gt; 這就是青春,熱血<br />\n黑人/南亞人 &gt; 搞搞震, 去試藥啦仆街<br />\n中國人 &gt; 蝗蟲性格係咁, 自卑變自大"},{"pid":"d8ab52f6d39ed86cdb52dcbe35083267943e82c7","tid":211160,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是但啦，反正啲憤世仇恨港女既連登仔實拉鬼佬落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n事實上港女會點先咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2fb87f0b8e7a50a463a7802a3f76a386677918","tid":211160,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"痴線， 連登班山番又批鬥乘客 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ea4680ac7947a9c6dfa072cb999dd793c916cc","tid":211160,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是但啦，反正啲憤世仇恨港女既連登仔實拉鬼佬落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ee2d6d6631e8382f735c20197118128d6719f5","tid":211160,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是但啦，反正啲憤世仇恨港女既連登仔實拉鬼佬落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n事實上港女會點先咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實重要咩"},{"pid":"a8e9d6e667d1f00ce20d8afad9e1368a35cdd011","tid":211160,"uid":70088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:02:02.000Z","msg